{"video_id": "M1HwvfEEzys", "title": "2018-01-17 | SB 3.27.5 | HG Amitasana Dasa", "speaker": "HG Amitasana Dasa", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M1HwvfEEzys", "duration": 1879, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 5.0, "text": " In this video, I will show you how to install and install Windows 10 on your PC."}, {"start": 5.0, "end": 10.0, "text": " First, open Windows 10."}, {"start": 10.0, "end": 15.0, "text": " Open Windows 10."}, {"start": 15.0, "end": 20.0, "text": " Open Windows 10."}, {"start": 20.0, "end": 25.0, "text": " Open Windows 10."}, {"start": 25.0, "end": 30.0, "text": " Open Windows 10."}, {"start": 30.0, "end": 35.0, "text": " Open Windows 10."}, {"start": 35.0, "end": 40.0, "text": " Open Windows 10."}, {"start": 40.0, "end": 45.0, "text": " Open Windows 10."}, {"start": 45.0, "end": 50.0, "text": " Open Windows 10."}, {"start": 50.0, "end": 55.0, "text": " Open Windows 10."}, {"start": 55.0, "end": 77.2, "text": " It is the duty of every conditioned soul to engage his polluted consciousness, that is our present predicament, we are polluted, our consciousness is polluted, which is now attached to material enjoyment, in very serious devotional service with detachment."}, {"start": 77.2, "end": 92.84, "text": " So that's what we are trying to do, trying to do, to engage in devotional service with detachment. Thus his mind and consciousness will be under full control, and that's our goal."}, {"start": 93.84, "end": 104.84, "text": " Right now our consciousness is polluted, it is dragged towards material enjoyment, towards material beauty. Our goal is by practicing the process of devotional service."}, {"start": 106.04, "end": 106.84, "text": " Our senses."}, {"start": 107.2, "end": 117.2, "text": " Our senses, our mind, our consciousness will get purified, and thereby our consciousness and mind will be in our control."}, {"start": 124.2, "end": 134.2, "text": " So here it is said polluted consciousness, among the 24 material elements, the 24th element is polluted consciousness."}, {"start": 137.20000000000002, "end": 155.20000000000002, "text": " We have the 5 working senses, 5 knowledge acquiring senses, 5 sense objects, 5 subtle cross elements, 3 subtle elements, and the 24th is polluted consciousness."}, {"start": 159.20000000000002, "end": 165.20000000000002, "text": " So now this polluted consciousness, how this polluted, how the consciousness which is originally pure,"}, {"start": 167.20000000000002, "end": 169.20000000000002, "text": " how it has become polluted."}, {"start": 170.20000000000002, "end": 176.20000000000002, "text": " So Prabhupada gives very nice, clear understanding in the purport."}, {"start": 177.20000000000002, "end": 187.20000000000002, "text": " This false thinking of false conditioned polluted consciousness is a result of contemplation on sense enjoyment."}, {"start": 189.20000000000002, "end": 191.20000000000002, "text": " As a result of false contemplation on sense enjoyment,"}, {"start": 191.20000000000002, "end": 193.20000000000002, "text": " As a result of false contemplation on sense enjoyment,"}, {"start": 193.20000000000002, "end": 195.20000000000002, "text": " As a result of false contemplation on sense enjoyment,"}, {"start": 195.20000000000002, "end": 212.20000000000002, "text": " one starts believing that I am the enjoyer, I am the proprietor."}, {"start": 212.20000000000002, "end": 216.20000000000002, "text": " This is the symptom of polluted consciousness."}, {"start": 216.20000000000002, "end": 220.20000000000002, "text": " I am the well-wisher of other living entities."}, {"start": 220.20000000000002, "end": 221.20000000000002, "text": " I am the well-wisher of other living entities."}, {"start": 221.20000000000002, "end": 223.20000000000002, "text": " I am the well-wisher of other living entities."}, {"start": 223.20000000000002, "end": 237.48000000000002, "text": " We see a lot of these days people, especially the rich people, it's now a very common trend, people committing 50% of their wealth."}, {"start": 237.48000000000002, "end": 248.50000000000003, "text": " It started with the joy of giving, Bill Gates pledging billions of dollars in charity."}, {"start": 248.5, "end": 259.48, "text": " And then many, many rich people followed, including Warren Buffet and so many rich people."}, {"start": 260.5, "end": 268.78, "text": " And when we look at them, it appears that, you know, they're so charitably disposed."}, {"start": 270.34, "end": 272.42, "text": " They're such wonderful human beings."}, {"start": 274.0, "end": 276.58, "text": " They're apparently not attached to their wealth."}, {"start": 276.58, "end": 289.65999999999997, "text": " They want to share their wealth with others, share their wealth to do good to the society, to uplift mankind, to help others, which is a very good sign."}, {"start": 290.38, "end": 291.44, "text": " It's a very good thing."}, {"start": 292.82, "end": 302.2, "text": " It is better than being very selfish and trying to hoard wealth and, you know, enjoy more and more."}, {"start": 306.58, "end": 310.78, "text": " Actually, as living entities, we have limitation as to how much we can enjoy."}, {"start": 313.41999999999996, "end": 324.41999999999996, "text": " Just like the typical example, if you see, if you want to eat rasgulla, you like rasgulla, you can eat two, three, four, up to four, you can really still enjoy."}, {"start": 327.41999999999996, "end": 330.36, "text": " And then sets in the law of diminishing returns."}, {"start": 333.86, "end": 336.36, "text": " The fifth rasgulla, you will..."}, {"start": 336.58, "end": 340.97999999999996, "text": " ...not like as much as you like the first one."}, {"start": 342.74, "end": 347.62, "text": " And then as you keep eating, sometimes, you know, you have those competitions, especially in hostels."}, {"start": 349.84, "end": 352.32, "text": " In mango mania, how many mangoes you can eat."}, {"start": 354.02, "end": 360.53999999999996, "text": " So, a time comes when one gets fed up."}, {"start": 364.53999999999996, "end": 366.41999999999996, "text": " So, many rich people, they have..."}, {"start": 366.58, "end": 368.58, "text": " ...you know, how much can you enjoy?"}, {"start": 368.58, "end": 376.58, "text": " Okay, at least we have hope, you know, I don't have a branded shirt, I don't have this thing, you know, common people, I don't have these shoes."}, {"start": 376.58, "end": 384.58, "text": " You know, if you reach a point, you have everything, you can buy anything, but still, you're not happy."}, {"start": 388.58, "end": 395.58, "text": " So then, just like here it says, polluted consciousness is, I am the enjoyer, that's the first thing, I want to enjoy matter."}, {"start": 396.58, "end": 401.65999999999997, "text": " Now, there's a limitation how much you can enjoy."}, {"start": 401.74, "end": 408.4, "text": " Just like we see, there's a saturation, even if you want to eat something, at one point of time, you cannot eat more."}, {"start": 410.12, "end": 413.06, "text": " That's how there's all this buffet, they are making money."}, {"start": 414.02, "end": 417.62, "text": " You know, they spread a lot, and finally a man can eat only 500, 600 grams."}, {"start": 418.84, "end": 421.78, "text": " That's the logic behind all this so-called buffet spread."}, {"start": 424.58, "end": 425.09999999999997, "text": " So..."}, {"start": 426.58, "end": 431.58, "text": " ...one wants to enjoy, but there's a limitation."}, {"start": 433.58, "end": 439.58, "text": " When I was in Bangalore many, many years back, I was staying with one of my relatives."}, {"start": 441.58, "end": 449.58, "text": " And there was a person, an expat from the US, who was staying in a five-star hotel here, Windsor Manor."}, {"start": 450.58, "end": 454.58, "text": " And he was staying in Windsor Manor for over six months, he was an Indian."}, {"start": 456.58, "end": 463.58, "text": " And, you know, heart of hearts, staying in Windsor Manor, six months, rich man."}, {"start": 463.58, "end": 471.58, "text": " Because typically when you go to, you know, five-star, it's all flashy, it's all decked up, it's all so comfortable."}, {"start": 471.58, "end": 475.58, "text": " So you really, I'm not enjoying, these people are enjoying so much."}, {"start": 475.58, "end": 478.58, "text": " You know, that's a conditioned soul's response."}, {"start": 480.58, "end": 484.58, "text": " And that person was invited one day for dinner at our place."}, {"start": 484.58, "end": 492.58, "text": " And he ate that simple food, rice, dal."}, {"start": 492.58, "end": 496.58, "text": " He especially requested, please make it simple, please make it simple."}, {"start": 496.58, "end": 500.58, "text": " I am longing to eat that simple dal and simple rice."}, {"start": 501.58, "end": 507.58, "text": " So he had that, and then he was, I mean, I was there at the dining table with him."}, {"start": 508.58, "end": 512.5799999999999, "text": " He said, it's so good, it's so tasty."}, {"start": 514.58, "end": 518.58, "text": " If you don't mind, he's practically, I could see, pleading."}, {"start": 519.58, "end": 523.58, "text": " Can I, you know, reluctantly, because how can you ask?"}, {"start": 524.58, "end": 528.58, "text": " Can I come maybe once in 10, 15 days?"}, {"start": 531.58, "end": 538.58, "text": " And then a cousin of mine says, yes, you can come, provided you invite us to Windsor Manor."}, {"start": 538.58, "end": 540.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 540.58, "end": 541.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 541.58, "end": 542.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 542.58, "end": 543.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 543.58, "end": 544.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 544.58, "end": 545.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 545.58, "end": 546.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 546.58, "end": 547.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 547.58, "end": 548.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 548.58, "end": 549.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 549.58, "end": 550.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 550.58, "end": 551.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 551.58, "end": 552.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 552.58, "end": 553.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 553.58, "end": 554.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 554.58, "end": 555.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 555.58, "end": 556.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 556.58, "end": 557.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 557.58, "end": 558.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 558.58, "end": 559.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 559.58, "end": 560.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 560.58, "end": 561.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 561.58, "end": 562.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 562.58, "end": 563.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 563.58, "end": 564.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 564.58, "end": 565.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 565.58, "end": 566.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 566.58, "end": 567.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 567.58, "end": 568.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 568.58, "end": 569.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 569.58, "end": 570.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 570.58, "end": 571.58, "text": " ."}, {"start": 571.58, "end": 580.58, "text": " We can't afford anything, many times we go to a hotel, we have limitations based on the budget, we have to decide, yeh nahi kha sakta, yeh bahut mehenga hai."}, {"start": 580.58, "end": 591.58, "text": " And imagine a person, the company is paying, he is one of the top CEOs, can eat anything."}, {"start": 591.58, "end": 598.58, "text": " Sometimes when feast is there, some limits are there, only two rasgullas per person, no limits."}, {"start": 598.58, "end": 601.58, "text": " The person is saying, can I eat simple food?"}, {"start": 601.58, "end": 605.58, "text": " So there are rich people who have done everything in life."}, {"start": 605.58, "end": 615.58, "text": " We still have hopes, we still have not gone on cruise, we still have not gone on X, still have not done this, still have not visited this country."}, {"start": 615.58, "end": 621.58, "text": " And we have heard about it, there are hopes of enjoyment, people who have done everything."}, {"start": 621.58, "end": 626.58, "text": " Can buy anything, can eat anything, can stay anywhere."}, {"start": 626.58, "end": 628.58, "text": " And still they find that something."}, {"start": 628.58, "end": 630.58, "text": " Nothing is lacking."}, {"start": 630.58, "end": 635.58, "text": " So such people, what do they do next?"}, {"start": 635.58, "end": 643.58, "text": " Bhoktaram, they have tried bhokta, there is a limitation, it is not satisfying intrinsically the soul."}, {"start": 643.58, "end": 646.58, "text": " Then they also try to lord over."}, {"start": 646.58, "end": 653.58, "text": " You know, you have become chairman and founder of a big multinational company."}, {"start": 653.58, "end": 656.58, "text": " It is the biggest company in the world."}, {"start": 656.58, "end": 657.58, "text": " Fortune 500."}, {"start": 658.58, "end": 661.58, "text": " You are the chairman."}, {"start": 661.58, "end": 666.58, "text": " If you are a manager in company, you want to be a CEO of that company, okay, that's done."}, {"start": 666.58, "end": 669.58, "text": " Then CEO of a bigger company."}, {"start": 669.58, "end": 670.58, "text": " Okay, then what?"}, {"start": 670.58, "end": 674.58, "text": " So you have become one of the best companies in the world."}, {"start": 674.58, "end": 676.58, "text": " So then what?"}, {"start": 676.58, "end": 678.58, "text": " You have seen that also."}, {"start": 678.58, "end": 683.58, "text": " People are at your beck and call, people are at your command."}, {"start": 683.58, "end": 685.58, "text": " You are very famous."}, {"start": 685.58, "end": 686.58, "text": " The next comes."}, {"start": 686.58, "end": 689.58, "text": " Suhridam sarva bhutanam."}, {"start": 692.58, "end": 694.58, "text": " Although it looks very nice."}, {"start": 694.58, "end": 695.58, "text": " Yes, it's nice in one sense."}, {"start": 695.58, "end": 696.58, "text": " We cannot ridicule."}, {"start": 696.58, "end": 698.58, "text": " It's a good sentiment to help others."}, {"start": 698.58, "end": 700.58, "text": " Compassion, daya."}, {"start": 700.58, "end": 705.58, "text": " When you see a person suffering, that's a natural human emotion to help others."}, {"start": 705.58, "end": 706.58, "text": " That's good."}, {"start": 706.58, "end": 715.58, "text": " But that doing good, that doing charity, that philanthropy with the mindset that I am supporting this cause."}, {"start": 716.58, "end": 722.58, "text": " I am feeding this hungry children."}, {"start": 722.58, "end": 731.58, "text": " When they get pictures of so many schools, children being fed, that inherent, Prabhupada says that is sense gratification only."}, {"start": 731.58, "end": 733.58, "text": " They get a sense of satisfaction."}, {"start": 733.58, "end": 737.58, "text": " So many children are getting fed because of me."}, {"start": 737.58, "end": 741.58, "text": " That's very fine enjoyment."}, {"start": 741.58, "end": 744.58, "text": " It's more than rasgulla enjoyment."}, {"start": 744.58, "end": 748.58, "text": " So many villages, there were no drinking water."}, {"start": 748.58, "end": 750.58, "text": " Now the drinking water has come."}, {"start": 750.58, "end": 756.58, "text": " So many villages have benefited because of me."}, {"start": 756.58, "end": 761.58, "text": " It's a finer sense gratification."}, {"start": 761.58, "end": 763.58, "text": " At the face value, it looks very good."}, {"start": 763.58, "end": 764.58, "text": " It is good."}, {"start": 764.58, "end": 765.58, "text": " We are not denying that."}, {"start": 765.58, "end": 769.58, "text": " But as a conditioned soul, there is a pollution in the consciousness."}, {"start": 769.58, "end": 770.58, "text": " I am the enjoyer."}, {"start": 770.58, "end": 772.58, "text": " I am the proprietor."}, {"start": 772.58, "end": 776.58, "text": " I am the well-wisher of all living entities."}, {"start": 776.58, "end": 781.58, "text": " Whereas Prabhupada here mentions, Krishna also mentions in the Gita,"}, {"start": 781.58, "end": 787.58, "text": " bhokta rāmyajña-suprasāṁ sarva-loka-maheśvaram suhṛdam sarva-bhūtānā"}, {"start": 787.58, "end": 796.58, "text": " One who understands, one who is convinced, one whose consciousness is pure, he understands that Krishna is the real enjoyer."}, {"start": 796.58, "end": 798.58, "text": " He is the bhokta."}, {"start": 798.58, "end": 800.58, "text": " He is the real enjoyer."}, {"start": 800.58, "end": 803.58, "text": " He is the real proprietor."}, {"start": 803.58, "end": 806.58, "text": " He is the one who is sarva-loka-maheśvaram."}, {"start": 806.58, "end": 809.58, "text": " And he is suhṛdam sarva-bhūtānā."}, {"start": 809.58, "end": 812.58, "text": " He is the well-wisher of all living entities."}, {"start": 812.58, "end": 823.58, "text": " Even when we want to help others, sometimes even so-called service borders between social service and this thing."}, {"start": 823.58, "end": 825.58, "text": " We also want to do good to society."}, {"start": 825.58, "end": 826.58, "text": " Paropakār."}, {"start": 826.58, "end": 828.58, "text": " Janma sārtak kari paropakār."}, {"start": 828.58, "end": 829.58, "text": " Paropakār."}, {"start": 829.58, "end": 838.58, "text": " Sometimes even Akshāpātra people say, you know, it's a social service, feeding to hungry child."}, {"start": 838.58, "end": 843.58, "text": " The problem is not in the act per se."}, {"start": 843.58, "end": 850.58, "text": " Problem is what is the consciousness behind that act."}, {"start": 850.58, "end": 855.58, "text": " With what consciousness we are doing that act."}, {"start": 855.58, "end": 857.58, "text": " If we are doing that act with the consciousness that,"}, {"start": 857.58, "end": 862.58, "text": " you know, I am supporting, I am feeding, I am doing this thing."}, {"start": 862.58, "end": 864.58, "text": " Then that is material consciousness."}, {"start": 864.58, "end": 866.58, "text": " Then that's a material activity."}, {"start": 866.58, "end": 869.58, "text": " Then that's a material service."}, {"start": 869.58, "end": 878.58, "text": " But if we are doing that with the understanding, with the consciousness that everyone is part and parcel of Krishna."}, {"start": 878.58, "end": 880.58, "text": " Krishna is the real maintainer."}, {"start": 880.58, "end": 881.58, "text": " Krishna is the real bhokta."}, {"start": 881.58, "end": 883.58, "text": " Krishna is the real proprietor."}, {"start": 883.58, "end": 886.58, "text": " And I am just an insignificant speck."}, {"start": 887.58, "end": 891.58, "text": " A part, an amsa, a servant."}, {"start": 891.58, "end": 897.58, "text": " And this is being done by Krishna through me."}, {"start": 897.58, "end": 900.58, "text": " Krishna is so kind that he is using me as an instrument."}, {"start": 900.58, "end": 905.58, "text": " Provided that service is authorized."}, {"start": 905.58, "end": 911.58, "text": " Then such service purifies us."}, {"start": 911.58, "end": 914.58, "text": " So Prabhupāda gives a very good thing."}, {"start": 914.58, "end": 916.58, "text": " Now our consciousness is polluted."}, {"start": 916.58, "end": 918.58, "text": " Our senses are contaminated."}, {"start": 918.58, "end": 920.58, "text": " They are dabbling in sense objects."}, {"start": 920.58, "end": 923.58, "text": " They have got attached to sense enjoyment."}, {"start": 923.58, "end": 926.58, "text": " And mind is also impure."}, {"start": 926.58, "end": 930.58, "text": " Now one thing is you restrict yourself."}, {"start": 930.58, "end": 931.58, "text": " Restrain yourself."}, {"start": 931.58, "end": 933.58, "text": " Not engage."}, {"start": 933.58, "end": 937.58, "text": " Not act in sinful ways."}, {"start": 937.58, "end": 940.58, "text": " So Prabhupāda says it's very difficult."}, {"start": 940.58, "end": 944.58, "text": " Viṣyāvinivartante nirahārasya dehinā."}, {"start": 946.58, "end": 949.58, "text": " So there are some so-called spiritualists"}, {"start": 949.58, "end": 953.58, "text": " or spiritualists who have tried to restrain their senses"}, {"start": 953.58, "end": 959.58, "text": " through yoga processes by abstaining the senses from sense objects."}, {"start": 959.58, "end": 962.58, "text": " Example is given of Viṣyamitra Muni."}, {"start": 962.58, "end": 966.58, "text": " But then the senses are even one of the roaming senses"}, {"start": 966.58, "end": 970.58, "text": " on which the mind focuses can carry away the person's intelligence."}, {"start": 970.58, "end": 974.58, "text": " So the process which Prabhupāda is doing,"}, {"start": 974.58, "end": 978.58, "text": " the process which Prabhupāda is so mercifully given to all of us"}, {"start": 978.58, "end": 984.58, "text": " is to engage our mind and senses in the service of the Lord."}, {"start": 984.58, "end": 987.58, "text": " We all have natural drives, natural inclinations."}, {"start": 987.58, "end": 989.58, "text": " We are all rādhsik in that sense."}, {"start": 989.58, "end": 991.58, "text": " A lot of passion."}, {"start": 991.58, "end": 993.58, "text": " We want to do so many things."}, {"start": 993.58, "end": 995.58, "text": " We want to achieve so many things."}, {"start": 995.58, "end": 999.58, "text": " Okay, do it for Kṛṣṇa."}, {"start": 999.58, "end": 1000.58, "text": " We want to create so many things."}, {"start": 1000.58, "end": 1002.58, "text": " Okay, create for Kṛṣṇa."}, {"start": 1002.58, "end": 1005.58, "text": " We engage the senses and the mind in the service of the Lord."}, {"start": 1005.58, "end": 1008.58, "text": " Gradually what happens is when we do that,"}, {"start": 1008.58, "end": 1012.58, "text": " the mind becomes pure, the senses become pure."}, {"start": 1012.58, "end": 1016.58, "text": " The consciousness, polluted consciousness, bhūkta, rāmas,"}, {"start": 1016.58, "end": 1020.58, "text": " and this service also is so wonderful when we do services."}, {"start": 1020.58, "end": 1023.58, "text": " Sometimes we, you know,"}, {"start": 1023.58, "end": 1026.58, "text": " when we go for collection, somebody will not give,"}, {"start": 1026.58, "end": 1031.58, "text": " somebody will chastise us, somebody will, you know, harass us."}, {"start": 1031.58, "end": 1036.58, "text": " In the process, or when we go for book distribution,"}, {"start": 1036.58, "end": 1040.58, "text": " sometimes a lot of books get sold, sometimes no book gets sold."}, {"start": 1040.58, "end": 1044.58, "text": " In the process, we are learning the fundamental principles."}, {"start": 1044.58, "end": 1048.58, "text": " What are the fundamental principles?"}, {"start": 1048.58, "end": 1051.58, "text": " That Kṛṣṇa is a real doer."}, {"start": 1051.58, "end": 1053.58, "text": " Kṛṣṇa is a real enjoyer."}, {"start": 1053.58, "end": 1056.58, "text": " Kṛṣṇa is a real proprietor."}, {"start": 1056.58, "end": 1059.58, "text": " Apart from the results what we are trying to achieve,"}, {"start": 1059.58, "end": 1062.58, "text": " Kṛṣṇa is working, Prabhupāda is working"}, {"start": 1062.58, "end": 1065.58, "text": " to teach us some very fundamental principles"}, {"start": 1065.58, "end": 1068.58, "text": " which will purify our consciousness."}, {"start": 1068.58, "end": 1071.58, "text": " Sometimes if we are not properly situated,"}, {"start": 1071.58, "end": 1074.58, "text": " we are overly focused on the results."}, {"start": 1074.58, "end": 1077.58, "text": " And success or failure is completely dependent on"}, {"start": 1077.58, "end": 1080.58, "text": " whether I have got the results or not."}, {"start": 1080.58, "end": 1083.58, "text": " But in devotional service, the beauty is"}, {"start": 1083.58, "end": 1086.58, "text": " even if so-called results are not there,"}, {"start": 1086.58, "end": 1088.58, "text": " the greatest benefit what we are getting"}, {"start": 1088.58, "end": 1090.58, "text": " by engaging in devotional service"}, {"start": 1090.58, "end": 1093.58, "text": " is purification of consciousness,"}, {"start": 1093.58, "end": 1096.58, "text": " irrespective of external results."}, {"start": 1096.58, "end": 1099.58, "text": " So in that sense, there is no loss,"}, {"start": 1099.58, "end": 1102.58, "text": " there is no diminution."}, {"start": 1102.58, "end": 1110.58, "text": " So what happens when we are dabbling in sense enjoyment?"}, {"start": 1110.58, "end": 1115.58, "text": " When there is a drive force enjoying the senses,"}, {"start": 1115.58, "end": 1117.58, "text": " that our ācāryas say is called"}, {"start": 1117.58, "end": 1122.58, "text": " kūṭam,"}, {"start": 1122.58, "end": 1126.58, "text": " that drive to enjoy."}, {"start": 1126.58, "end": 1128.58, "text": " Arjuna also asked Kṛṣṇa,"}, {"start": 1128.58, "end": 1131.58, "text": " why is it, Kṛṣṇa, that sometimes we are forced"}, {"start": 1131.58, "end": 1135.58, "text": " to act in sinful ways much against our wish?"}, {"start": 1135.58, "end": 1138.58, "text": " Even we realize in our day-to-day life,"}, {"start": 1138.58, "end": 1141.58, "text": " on one side we want to get up early in the morning,"}, {"start": 1141.58, "end": 1143.58, "text": " the other side, when we get up in the morning,"}, {"start": 1143.58, "end": 1146.58, "text": " when the alarm rings, there is another force"}, {"start": 1146.58, "end": 1152.58, "text": " which says, no, let me sleep."}, {"start": 1152.58, "end": 1155.58, "text": " So Kṛṣṇa was asked, what is that force?"}, {"start": 1155.58, "end": 1157.58, "text": " Why is it that many times we act in sinful ways"}, {"start": 1157.58, "end": 1159.58, "text": " much against our wish,"}, {"start": 1159.58, "end": 1166.58, "text": " as if there is some kind of a push?"}, {"start": 1166.58, "end": 1171.58, "text": " So that push is called kūṭam,"}, {"start": 1171.58, "end": 1175.58, "text": " and that kūṭam results in actions,"}, {"start": 1175.58, "end": 1178.58, "text": " we act based on that force,"}, {"start": 1178.58, "end": 1184.58, "text": " and that actions deposit the reaction in our system,"}, {"start": 1184.58, "end": 1189.58, "text": " and that reactions are deposited in the form of bījam,"}, {"start": 1189.58, "end": 1195.58, "text": " the seed, bījam."}, {"start": 1195.58, "end": 1197.58, "text": " And just like in a seed,"}, {"start": 1197.58, "end": 1200.58, "text": " we see different seed sprouts at different times,"}, {"start": 1200.58, "end": 1204.58, "text": " some seeds sprout in one day,"}, {"start": 1204.58, "end": 1207.58, "text": " some seed sprouts in four days."}, {"start": 1207.58, "end": 1210.58, "text": " So likewise, this bījam"}, {"start": 1210.58, "end": 1213.58, "text": " fructifies into reaction,"}, {"start": 1213.58, "end": 1217.58, "text": " which manifests in the life as enjoyment or suffering,"}, {"start": 1217.58, "end": 1219.58, "text": " which is called a stage of falon mukham,"}, {"start": 1219.58, "end": 1220.58, "text": " falā,"}, {"start": 1220.58, "end": 1224.58, "text": " falā of the actions which we have done,"}, {"start": 1224.58, "end": 1228.58, "text": " and that stage is called falon mukham."}, {"start": 1228.58, "end": 1230.58, "text": " So what we are seeing,"}, {"start": 1230.58, "end": 1233.58, "text": " different people enjoying and suffering differently,"}, {"start": 1233.58, "end": 1240.58, "text": " is what has started manifesting in their life."}, {"start": 1240.58, "end": 1242.58, "text": " Sometimes people get bewildered"}, {"start": 1242.58, "end": 1245.58, "text": " when they see good people suffering"}, {"start": 1245.58, "end": 1248.58, "text": " or bad people enjoying life."}, {"start": 1248.58, "end": 1250.58, "text": " That's because,"}, {"start": 1250.58, "end": 1253.58, "text": " even though at present they are doing good,"}, {"start": 1253.58, "end": 1255.58, "text": " but there are a lot of bījams"}, {"start": 1255.58, "end": 1258.58, "text": " which are stored from the actions done in the past,"}, {"start": 1258.58, "end": 1261.58, "text": " which are now fructifying."}, {"start": 1261.58, "end": 1264.58, "text": " A person may have done good in the past,"}, {"start": 1264.58, "end": 1267.58, "text": " as a result there are good bījams stored,"}, {"start": 1267.58, "end": 1270.58, "text": " but currently he may be doing bad things,"}, {"start": 1270.58, "end": 1272.58, "text": " but still he may be enjoying"}, {"start": 1272.58, "end": 1276.58, "text": " the reactions of the past deeds."}, {"start": 1276.58, "end": 1278.58, "text": " And vice versa,"}, {"start": 1278.58, "end": 1281.58, "text": " for a person who is doing good now,"}, {"start": 1281.58, "end": 1283.58, "text": " could be result of,"}, {"start": 1283.58, "end": 1285.58, "text": " still could be suffering because of"}, {"start": 1285.58, "end": 1288.58, "text": " the actions done in the past."}, {"start": 1291.58, "end": 1296.58, "text": " Now ācāryas have even gone further,"}, {"start": 1296.58, "end": 1301.58, "text": " just like in any other field of activity,"}, {"start": 1301.58, "end": 1304.58, "text": " they do root cause analysis."}, {"start": 1304.58, "end": 1305.58, "text": " What is the cause?"}, {"start": 1305.58, "end": 1306.58, "text": " What is the cause?"}, {"start": 1306.58, "end": 1308.58, "text": " What is the cause?"}, {"start": 1308.58, "end": 1311.58, "text": " So ācāryas have analyzed kūtam."}, {"start": 1311.58, "end": 1317.58, "text": " Kūtam is that which forces us to act in sinful ways."}, {"start": 1317.58, "end": 1320.58, "text": " Sinful ways or whatever,"}, {"start": 1320.58, "end": 1323.58, "text": " forces us to act."}, {"start": 1323.58, "end": 1327.58, "text": " So they have analyzed what is"}, {"start": 1327.58, "end": 1330.58, "text": " a step behind kūtam."}, {"start": 1335.58, "end": 1338.58, "text": " That force is called kāma,"}, {"start": 1338.58, "end": 1340.58, "text": " lust."}, {"start": 1340.58, "end": 1344.58, "text": " Here it says desire to enjoy the senses."}, {"start": 1344.58, "end": 1346.58, "text": " What is lust?"}, {"start": 1346.58, "end": 1349.58, "text": " Desire to enjoy independent of Kṛṣṇa."}, {"start": 1350.58, "end": 1352.58, "text": " And they have gone one step ahead"}, {"start": 1352.58, "end": 1354.58, "text": " and realized what is the cause of that lust,"}, {"start": 1354.58, "end": 1356.58, "text": " desire,"}, {"start": 1356.58, "end": 1357.58, "text": " which results in kūtam,"}, {"start": 1357.58, "end": 1358.58, "text": " which results in bījam,"}, {"start": 1358.58, "end": 1360.58, "text": " which results in falonmukham."}, {"start": 1360.58, "end": 1364.58, "text": " And they found out"}, {"start": 1364.58, "end": 1368.58, "text": " that the result of that lust,"}, {"start": 1368.58, "end": 1369.58, "text": " or kāma,"}, {"start": 1369.58, "end": 1371.58, "text": " is avidyā."}, {"start": 1371.58, "end": 1372.58, "text": " In Bhāgavatam it is mentioned,"}, {"start": 1372.58, "end": 1376.58, "text": " avidyā kāma karma bhī."}, {"start": 1376.58, "end": 1377.58, "text": " Because of avidyā,"}, {"start": 1377.58, "end": 1379.58, "text": " this knowledge,"}, {"start": 1379.58, "end": 1381.58, "text": " the true knowledge,"}, {"start": 1381.58, "end": 1383.58, "text": " who I am,"}, {"start": 1383.58, "end": 1386.58, "text": " I am amsa of Kṛṣṇa,"}, {"start": 1386.58, "end": 1389.58, "text": " I am not the bhoktā,"}, {"start": 1389.58, "end": 1393.58, "text": " I am a small insignificant servant,"}, {"start": 1393.58, "end": 1394.58, "text": " dāsu asmi."}, {"start": 1394.58, "end": 1396.58, "text": " Because of this avidyā,"}, {"start": 1396.58, "end": 1400.58, "text": " Prabhupāda also says,"}, {"start": 1400.58, "end": 1403.58, "text": " why this contaminated consciousness comes about?"}, {"start": 1403.58, "end": 1406.58, "text": " Because of contemplation on sense enjoyment."}, {"start": 1406.58, "end": 1408.58, "text": " Sense enjoyment,"}, {"start": 1408.58, "end": 1409.58, "text": " independent of Kṛṣṇa,"}, {"start": 1409.58, "end": 1411.58, "text": " is lust."}, {"start": 1411.58, "end": 1414.58, "text": " That results in avidyā,"}, {"start": 1414.58, "end": 1418.58, "text": " false understanding about ourself."}, {"start": 1418.58, "end": 1419.58, "text": " I am the enjoyer,"}, {"start": 1419.58, "end": 1420.58, "text": " I am bhoktā,"}, {"start": 1420.58, "end": 1426.58, "text": " I am the proprietor."}, {"start": 1426.58, "end": 1427.58, "text": " So avidyā,"}, {"start": 1427.58, "end": 1428.58, "text": " kāma,"}, {"start": 1428.58, "end": 1430.58, "text": " results in kāma,"}, {"start": 1430.58, "end": 1432.58, "text": " and karma bhī."}, {"start": 1432.58, "end": 1433.58, "text": " We act,"}, {"start": 1433.58, "end": 1435.58, "text": " that deposits bījam,"}, {"start": 1435.58, "end": 1437.58, "text": " and then chain of actions and reactions,"}, {"start": 1437.58, "end": 1442.58, "text": " and then the living entity gets entangled"}, {"start": 1442.58, "end": 1444.58, "text": " in enjoyment and suffering"}, {"start": 1444.58, "end": 1446.58, "text": " in this material world."}, {"start": 1446.58, "end": 1448.58, "text": " To relieve ourselves of that suffering,"}, {"start": 1448.58, "end": 1450.58, "text": " we further act."}, {"start": 1450.58, "end": 1453.58, "text": " Those actions further create reactions."}, {"start": 1453.58, "end": 1455.58, "text": " While we are enjoying or suffering"}, {"start": 1455.58, "end": 1457.58, "text": " the reactions of the past,"}, {"start": 1457.58, "end": 1459.58, "text": " to counteract those enjoyment and suffering,"}, {"start": 1459.58, "end": 1460.58, "text": " we further act,"}, {"start": 1460.58, "end": 1461.58, "text": " and like that,"}, {"start": 1461.58, "end": 1463.58, "text": " the action and reaction,"}, {"start": 1463.58, "end": 1466.58, "text": " one gets completely entangled."}, {"start": 1467.58, "end": 1469.58, "text": " So what devotional service does,"}, {"start": 1469.58, "end": 1470.58, "text": " here it says,"}, {"start": 1470.58, "end": 1473.58, "text": " one should very seriously engage in devotional service"}, {"start": 1473.58, "end": 1476.58, "text": " with detachment."}, {"start": 1476.58, "end": 1477.58, "text": " So devotional service,"}, {"start": 1477.58, "end": 1479.58, "text": " one thing what it does is,"}, {"start": 1479.58, "end": 1483.58, "text": " it not only burns to ashes the bījams,"}, {"start": 1483.58, "end": 1487.58, "text": " the reactions of the deeds what we have done in the past,"}, {"start": 1487.58, "end": 1490.58, "text": " it creates no further reactions,"}, {"start": 1490.58, "end": 1493.58, "text": " no further bījam,"}, {"start": 1493.58, "end": 1495.58, "text": " and,"}, {"start": 1495.58, "end": 1499.58, "text": " it destroys kāma,"}, {"start": 1499.58, "end": 1503.58, "text": " and also destroys avidhyā."}, {"start": 1505.58, "end": 1508.58, "text": " There are so many things which we can do,"}, {"start": 1508.58, "end": 1509.58, "text": " prāyaścitta,"}, {"start": 1509.58, "end": 1512.58, "text": " whereby we can take care of"}, {"start": 1512.58, "end": 1514.58, "text": " the reactions."}, {"start": 1514.58, "end": 1516.58, "text": " By doing some yajñas,"}, {"start": 1516.58, "end": 1518.58, "text": " by doing some homas,"}, {"start": 1518.58, "end": 1522.58, "text": " we can nullify those reactions."}, {"start": 1525.58, "end": 1528.58, "text": " But,"}, {"start": 1528.58, "end": 1531.58, "text": " that force which,"}, {"start": 1531.58, "end": 1533.58, "text": " you know,"}, {"start": 1533.58, "end": 1535.58, "text": " helplessly makes us act"}, {"start": 1535.58, "end": 1537.58, "text": " in sinful ways,"}, {"start": 1537.58, "end": 1540.58, "text": " that avidhyā,"}, {"start": 1540.58, "end": 1542.58, "text": " the ignorance of the self,"}, {"start": 1542.58, "end": 1545.58, "text": " ignorance of our true constitutional position,"}, {"start": 1545.58, "end": 1547.58, "text": " still is not addressed."}, {"start": 1550.58, "end": 1552.58, "text": " So devotional service,"}, {"start": 1552.58, "end": 1553.58, "text": " bhakti yoga,"}, {"start": 1553.58, "end": 1556.58, "text": " by taking shelter of Kṛṣṇa,"}, {"start": 1556.58, "end": 1561.58, "text": " shelter of a pure devotee,"}, {"start": 1561.58, "end": 1565.58, "text": " we are not only burning all the sinful reactions of the past,"}, {"start": 1565.58, "end": 1567.58, "text": " creating no further reactions,"}, {"start": 1567.58, "end": 1570.58, "text": " because bhakti is akarma."}, {"start": 1570.58, "end": 1573.58, "text": " It doesn't create any good or bad reactions."}, {"start": 1573.58, "end": 1575.58, "text": " It destroys avidhyā,"}, {"start": 1575.58, "end": 1577.58, "text": " destroys kāma,"}, {"start": 1577.58, "end": 1581.58, "text": " cleans up our consciousness."}, {"start": 1581.58, "end": 1582.58, "text": " So that is,"}, {"start": 1582.58, "end": 1584.58, "text": " so when we are engaging in devotional service,"}, {"start": 1584.58, "end": 1586.58, "text": " when we are,"}, {"start": 1586.58, "end": 1590.58, "text": " when we are practising the process of Kṛṣṇa consciousness,"}, {"start": 1590.58, "end": 1592.58, "text": " we should have this knowledge,"}, {"start": 1592.58, "end": 1594.58, "text": " what we are doing."}, {"start": 1594.58, "end": 1596.58, "text": " What is the goal?"}, {"start": 1596.58, "end": 1598.58, "text": " What are we trying to achieve?"}, {"start": 1598.58, "end": 1602.58, "text": " Sometimes we can become very mechanical in our service,"}, {"start": 1602.58, "end": 1604.58, "text": " simply morning to evening doing something,"}, {"start": 1604.58, "end": 1605.58, "text": " carrying a bag,"}, {"start": 1605.58, "end": 1607.58, "text": " going here and there."}, {"start": 1608.58, "end": 1610.58, "text": " We are engaging in devotional service,"}, {"start": 1610.58, "end": 1611.58, "text": " service of the Lord."}, {"start": 1611.58, "end": 1613.58, "text": " The Lord is having a mission in this world."}, {"start": 1613.58, "end": 1615.58, "text": " We are part of that mission."}, {"start": 1615.58, "end": 1617.58, "text": " And in the process,"}, {"start": 1617.58, "end": 1619.58, "text": " we are getting purified."}, {"start": 1620.58, "end": 1621.58, "text": " Let's stop here."}, {"start": 1621.58, "end": 1622.58, "text": " Anyone has any question,"}, {"start": 1622.58, "end": 1624.58, "text": " anything like to ask?"}, {"start": 1631.58, "end": 1633.58, "text": " You can ask."}, {"start": 1641.58, "end": 1646.58, "text": " All of us,"}, {"start": 1646.58, "end": 1648.58, "text": " we are engaged in devotional service,"}, {"start": 1648.58, "end": 1650.58, "text": " but particularly,"}, {"start": 1650.58, "end": 1652.58, "text": " if consciousness is polluted,"}, {"start": 1652.58, "end": 1654.58, "text": " and with that consciousness,"}, {"start": 1654.58, "end": 1656.58, "text": " how to bring detachment in that service?"}, {"start": 1656.58, "end": 1658.58, "text": " Because consciousness is,"}, {"start": 1658.58, "end": 1659.58, "text": " again,"}, {"start": 1659.58, "end": 1660.58, "text": " fruitive mentality."}, {"start": 1660.58, "end": 1662.58, "text": " If I am doing also devotional service,"}, {"start": 1662.58, "end": 1664.58, "text": " I am expecting some result,"}, {"start": 1664.58, "end": 1665.58, "text": " some fruitive,"}, {"start": 1665.58, "end": 1667.58, "text": " my mind is acting in that direction only,"}, {"start": 1667.58, "end": 1668.58, "text": " some honour,"}, {"start": 1668.58, "end": 1670.58, "text": " something I want out of it."}, {"start": 1670.58, "end": 1672.58, "text": " So with polluted consciousness,"}, {"start": 1672.58, "end": 1674.58, "text": " how to practice this thing,"}, {"start": 1674.58, "end": 1677.58, "text": " how to bring this element of detachment?"}, {"start": 1677.58, "end": 1680.58, "text": " So this purification of consciousness"}, {"start": 1680.58, "end": 1682.58, "text": " is inbuilt in the system."}, {"start": 1686.58, "end": 1687.58, "text": " One thing is,"}, {"start": 1687.58, "end": 1688.58, "text": " the world has been designed"}, {"start": 1688.58, "end": 1690.58, "text": " so beautifully by the Lord,"}, {"start": 1691.58, "end": 1694.58, "text": " when you act in wrong way,"}, {"start": 1694.58, "end": 1695.58, "text": " it will backfire."}, {"start": 1695.58, "end": 1702.58, "text": " When you want to act as an enjoyer,"}, {"start": 1702.58, "end": 1704.58, "text": " act as a proprietor,"}, {"start": 1704.58, "end": 1708.58, "text": " it will hit you back,"}, {"start": 1708.58, "end": 1711.58, "text": " even as devotees."}, {"start": 1711.58, "end": 1712.58, "text": " That's why Krishna said,"}, {"start": 1712.58, "end": 1714.58, "text": " bhau naam janma naam ante,"}, {"start": 1714.58, "end": 1715.58, "text": " jnan maante."}, {"start": 1715.58, "end": 1717.58, "text": " After many times getting hit,"}, {"start": 1717.58, "end": 1718.58, "text": " why not?"}, {"start": 1720.58, "end": 1721.58, "text": " And now I realise,"}, {"start": 1721.58, "end": 1723.58, "text": " I am not the enjoyer."}, {"start": 1723.58, "end": 1725.58, "text": " So we will start doing devotional service,"}, {"start": 1725.58, "end": 1726.58, "text": " with that same consciousness,"}, {"start": 1726.58, "end": 1727.58, "text": " I am the enjoyer."}, {"start": 1727.58, "end": 1730.58, "text": " I want to enjoy peace of mind."}, {"start": 1731.58, "end": 1732.58, "text": " I want to enjoy"}, {"start": 1732.58, "end": 1734.58, "text": " lording over bhaktas."}, {"start": 1735.58, "end": 1736.58, "text": " We start with that."}, {"start": 1737.58, "end": 1738.58, "text": " You cannot help it."}, {"start": 1738.58, "end": 1740.58, "text": " Theoretically it will not help."}, {"start": 1741.58, "end": 1742.58, "text": " From today onwards,"}, {"start": 1742.58, "end": 1743.58, "text": " I will not enjoy."}, {"start": 1743.58, "end": 1744.58, "text": " From today onwards,"}, {"start": 1744.58, "end": 1745.58, "text": " I will not think I am the proprietor."}, {"start": 1745.58, "end": 1746.58, "text": " It doesn't happen."}, {"start": 1747.58, "end": 1749.58, "text": " It will be at a mental level."}, {"start": 1750.58, "end": 1752.58, "text": " So we engage in devotional service,"}, {"start": 1752.58, "end": 1753.58, "text": " just like, you know,"}, {"start": 1753.58, "end": 1754.58, "text": " diamonds get rubbed,"}, {"start": 1754.58, "end": 1756.58, "text": " so this rubbing will go on here also."}, {"start": 1758.58, "end": 1759.58, "text": " So we will collect,"}, {"start": 1759.58, "end": 1760.58, "text": " we will think that I am a big collector,"}, {"start": 1760.58, "end": 1762.58, "text": " finally you will get a hit."}, {"start": 1764.58, "end": 1766.58, "text": " No, I am not the collector."}, {"start": 1768.58, "end": 1769.58, "text": " You go for book distribution,"}, {"start": 1769.58, "end": 1771.58, "text": " one day you will distribute a lot of books,"}, {"start": 1771.58, "end": 1772.58, "text": " wow,"}, {"start": 1772.58, "end": 1773.58, "text": " you get a feeling,"}, {"start": 1773.58, "end": 1774.58, "text": " I am a good,"}, {"start": 1774.58, "end": 1775.58, "text": " I am very expert,"}, {"start": 1775.58, "end": 1776.58, "text": " very nice."}, {"start": 1776.58, "end": 1777.58, "text": " See, I convinced him."}, {"start": 1777.58, "end": 1778.58, "text": " Next day you do all your convincing,"}, {"start": 1778.58, "end": 1780.58, "text": " and nobody will buy a book."}, {"start": 1781.58, "end": 1782.58, "text": " Then you realise,"}, {"start": 1782.58, "end": 1783.58, "text": " my God, it's a fact,"}, {"start": 1783.58, "end": 1784.58, "text": " I am not the convincer."}, {"start": 1785.58, "end": 1787.58, "text": " This happens over a period of time."}, {"start": 1788.58, "end": 1790.58, "text": " And while we are engaged in devotional service,"}, {"start": 1790.58, "end": 1791.58, "text": " slowly,"}, {"start": 1791.58, "end": 1792.58, "text": " dhire dhire,"}, {"start": 1792.58, "end": 1793.58, "text": " dhire dhire,"}, {"start": 1793.58, "end": 1794.58, "text": " that purification happens."}, {"start": 1794.58, "end": 1796.58, "text": " One comes to our senses."}, {"start": 1797.58, "end": 1799.58, "text": " Unfortunately,"}, {"start": 1799.58, "end": 1800.58, "text": " to some extent,"}, {"start": 1800.58, "end": 1801.58, "text": " you can fast track the process,"}, {"start": 1801.58, "end": 1803.58, "text": " otherwise it will take time."}, {"start": 1803.58, "end": 1804.58, "text": " That's why it's a dhairiya,"}, {"start": 1804.58, "end": 1805.58, "text": " patience."}, {"start": 1806.58, "end": 1808.58, "text": " You start with polluted consciousness,"}, {"start": 1808.58, "end": 1809.58, "text": " as we engage,"}, {"start": 1809.58, "end": 1811.58, "text": " the purification of consciousness"}, {"start": 1811.58, "end": 1812.58, "text": " is inbuilt in the system."}, {"start": 1813.58, "end": 1815.58, "text": " For that,"}, {"start": 1815.58, "end": 1816.58, "text": " what we have to do,"}, {"start": 1816.58, "end": 1817.58, "text": " we have to,"}, {"start": 1817.58, "end": 1818.58, "text": " we have to,"}, {"start": 1818.58, "end": 1819.58, "text": " the process,"}, {"start": 1819.58, "end": 1820.58, "text": " shravanam,"}, {"start": 1820.58, "end": 1821.58, "text": " hearing,"}, {"start": 1821.58, "end": 1822.58, "text": " shunvata,"}, {"start": 1822.58, "end": 1823.58, "text": " swakataha,"}, {"start": 1823.58, "end": 1824.58, "text": " krishna,"}, {"start": 1824.58, "end": 1825.58, "text": " punya,"}, {"start": 1825.58, "end": 1826.58, "text": " shravana,"}, {"start": 1826.58, "end": 1827.58, "text": " kirtana,"}, {"start": 1827.58, "end": 1828.58, "text": " nashta,"}, {"start": 1828.58, "end": 1829.58, "text": " praesho,"}, {"start": 1829.58, "end": 1830.58, "text": " badreshu,"}, {"start": 1830.58, "end": 1831.58, "text": " nityam,"}, {"start": 1831.58, "end": 1832.58, "text": " bhagavata,"}, {"start": 1832.58, "end": 1833.58, "text": " sevaya,"}, {"start": 1833.58, "end": 1834.58, "text": " when we do that,"}, {"start": 1834.58, "end": 1835.58, "text": " all this abhadras,"}, {"start": 1835.58, "end": 1836.58, "text": " dirty things,"}, {"start": 1836.58, "end": 1837.58, "text": " which is clinging to us,"}, {"start": 1837.58, "end": 1838.58, "text": " clinging to our consciousness,"}, {"start": 1838.58, "end": 1839.58, "text": " which has overpowered our consciousness,"}, {"start": 1839.58, "end": 1840.58, "text": " completely gets subsided."}, {"start": 1840.58, "end": 1841.58, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 1841.58, "end": 1842.58, "text": " we have to,"}, {"start": 1842.58, "end": 1843.58, "text": " just like diamond,"}, {"start": 1843.58, "end": 1844.58, "text": " it's actually a very precious stone,"}, {"start": 1844.58, "end": 1845.58, "text": " but when you see original,"}, {"start": 1845.58, "end": 1846.58, "text": " this thing,"}, {"start": 1846.58, "end": 1847.58, "text": " it is unpolished,"}, {"start": 1847.58, "end": 1848.58, "text": " uncut,"}, {"start": 1848.58, "end": 1849.58, "text": " it is not shiny,"}, {"start": 1849.58, "end": 1850.58, "text": " but because of that polish,"}, {"start": 1850.58, "end": 1851.58, "text": " because of rubbing,"}, {"start": 1851.58, "end": 1852.58, "text": " because of different treatment,"}, {"start": 1852.58, "end": 1853.58, "text": " it goes through,"}, {"start": 1853.58, "end": 1854.58, "text": " it starts shining."}, {"start": 1854.58, "end": 1855.58, "text": " Same is the case,"}, {"start": 1855.58, "end": 1856.58, "text": " what happens with us."}, {"start": 1856.58, "end": 1857.58, "text": " Okay?"}, {"start": 1857.58, "end": 1858.58, "text": " Stop here."}, {"start": 1858.58, "end": 1859.58, "text": " Grantharaj,"}, {"start": 1859.58, "end": 1860.58, "text": " Srimad Bhagavatam ki,"}, {"start": 1860.58, "end": 1861.58, "text": " Srila Prabhupada."}, {"start": 1872.58, "end": 1898.58, "text": " Thank you."}]}